## Rank based
Consider a Memory with size $N$. The experience should by drawn prioritized 
after the index $i$ with probability $p_{i}=\frac{i}{\sum_{j=1}^{N}j}$.

Hierf√ºr definiere $S(n):=\sum_{i=1}^{N}i=\frac{n^{2}+n}{2}$